# upstream code). We do NOT vendor it — agent-browser is installed separately
# via `npm install -g agent-browser`. Ignored so an accidental clone in this
# path isn't tracked. The only agent-browser-related thing we DO commit is
# the MCP wrapper at competitors/agent-browser-mcp/.
